title: Reims vs Toulouse - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 30

title: PSG vs Le Havre - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 30

This is their second best clean sheet ratio against the same opponent among they’ve teams faced at least 30 times in the top-flight after Brest. Paris SG have lost only one of their 15 home matches against Le Havre in Ligue 1, 0-2 on 24 January 1998 with a brace from Cyrille Pouget.

title: Olympique Marseille vs Montpellier - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 30

title: Saint-Étienne vs Olympique Lyonnais - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 30
description: This will be the 125th derby between St Etienne and Lyon in all competitions. Les Gones have kept 41 clean sheets in those games, more than against any other team in their history. Lyon have won 11 of their 18 trips to St Etienne in Ligue 1 in the 21st century, being the team that has beaten Les Verts the most in Geoffroy-Guichard over the period.

title: Brest vs Lens - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 30
description: Brest have lost each of their last two games against Lens in Ligue 1 and could suffer three consecutive defeats for the first time in their history against this opponent in the top-flight. Brest have a 69% home win rate against Lens in Ligue 1, their highest percentage against a club they have played at home at least 10 times. RCL could become the first team that Brest manage to beat 10 times at home in Ligue 1.
